<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>DAUL | Built Different</title>
<style>
body{margin:0;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;background:#0d0d0d;color:#fff}
header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:20px 30px;background:#111}
.logo{color:#f0a020;font-size:28px;font-weight:bold}
nav a{color:white;text-decoration:none;margin-left:15px}
.hero{text-align:center;padding:80px 20px}
.hero h1{font-size:55px;margin:10px 0}
.accent{color:#f0a020}
.button{display:inline-block;background:#f0a020;color:#111;padding:12px 24px;border-radius:30px;text-decoration:none;font-weight:bold;margin-top:20px}
section{padding:50px 20px;max-width:900px;margin:auto}
.cards{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(180px,1fr));gap:15px}
.card{background:#1a1a1a;padding:20px;border-radius:12px}
footer{text-align:center;padding:30px;background:#111}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
<div class="logo">DAUL</div>
<nav>
<a href="#about">About</a>
<a href="#collections">Collections</a>
<a href="#contact">Contact</a>
</nav>
</header>

<section class="hero">
<p class="accent">Luxury × Streetwear</p>
<h1>BUILT DIFFERENT</h1>
<p>Premium streetwear designed to inspire confidence, comfort and elegance.</p>
<a class="button" href="#about">Explore DAUL</a>
</section>

<section id="about">
<h2 class="accent">Our Story</h2>
<p>DAUL was created from a simple idea: clothing should do more than cover you—it should change how you feel. Every piece is designed to help you feel more confident, comfortable and elegant.</p>
</section>

<section id="collections">
<h2 class="accent">Future Collections</h2>
<div class="cards">
<div class="card">Premium T-Shirts</div>
<div class="card">Hoodies</div>
<div class="card">Tracksuits</div>
<div class="card">Accessories</div>
</div>
</section>

<section id="contact">
<h2 class="accent">Connect With DAUL</h2>
<p><strong>TikTok:</strong> @daul.n0w</p>
<p>More ways to connect are coming soon.</p>
</section>

<footer>
<p>© 2026 DAUL • Built Different</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
